      <div class="hero-right">
        <p>We've built outbound engines from scratch for founders across food &amp; bev, B2B SaaS, and professional services. <strong>Not templates. Not playbooks. Actual running systems.</strong></p>
        <p>CRM, lead lists, cold email infrastructure, sequences, pipeline stages, hiring support — whatever the gap is, we close it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule">

<!-- PROOF — lead with the real thing -->
<section class="proof">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="proof-label">Case Study</div>
    <div class="proof-card sr sr-up">
      <div>
        <div class="proof-quote">"We went from zero outbound to converting roughly a hundred restaurants in about four months. The system Impello built wasn't just lead gen — it was the whole machine. CRM, sequences, call scripts, pipeline. We still run it today."</div>
        <div class="proof-who">
          <div class="proof-avatar">T</div>
          <div>
            <div class="proof-name">Tyler</div>
            <div class="proof-role">Founder, ReadySetMushrooms</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-sidebar">
        <h4>Results</h4>
        <div class="proof-stats">
          <div>
            <div class="proof-stat-val">~100</div>
            <div class="proof-stat-label">restaurants converted to trial</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="proof-stat-val">25%</div>
            <div class="proof-stat-label">outreach-to-conversion rate</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="proof-stat-val">400+</div>
            <div class="proof-stat-label">contacts called</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="proof-stat-val">Full stack</div>
            <div class="proof-stat-label">HubSpot, Apollo, email infra</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule">

<!-- WHAT WE DO -->
<section class="what" id="what">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="what-top">
      <h2 class="sr sr-up">Here's what we actually do</h2>
      <div class="what-blurb sr sr-up" style="transition-delay:.08s">
        <p>Most founders know they need "outbound" but don't have the infrastructure to run it. No CRM. No sequences. No defined ICP. Maybe a spreadsheet with some names in it.</p>
        <p>We come in and build the whole thing — then teach you to run it yourself or help you hire someone who can.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="what-grid">
      <div class="what-card tall sr sr-left">
        <div>
          <div class="what-card-num">01</div>
          <h3>Audit &amp; strategy</h3>
          <p>We map your current process (or lack thereof), define your ICP, research your market, and build a prioritized action plan. This alone is worth the call.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:40px">
          <div class="what-card-num">02</div>
          <h3>System buildout</h3>
          <p>CRM configuration, lead list curation, cold email warm-up and infrastructure, multi-step sequences, pipeline stages, automations. Everything you need to start generating conversations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="what-card sr sr-up" style="margin-bottom:24px">
          <div class="what-card-num">03</div>
          <h3>Launch &amp; iterate</h3>
          <p>We go live, monitor what's working, rewrite what isn't, and keep optimizing until the system runs without us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="what-card sr sr-up" style="transition-delay:.1s">
          <h3>Ongoing &amp; fractional</h3>
          <p>Need us to stick around? We offer monthly retainers for continued optimization, and fractional sales leadership if you're building a team. Most clients start with a buildout and expand from there.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="rule">

<!-- PRICING -->
<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pricing-top sr sr-up">
      <h2>Pricing</h2>
      <p>Three ways to work together. All designed to pay for themselves within 90 days.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing-layout">
      <div class="p-card sr sr-up">
        <div class="p-tier">Tier 1</div>
        <div class="p-name">Sales System Buildout</div>
        <div class="p-desc">Go from nothing to a running outbound system in 4–6 weeks.</div>
        <div class="p-price">$4–8k <span>project</span></div>
        <div class="p-note">One-time. Scope-dependent.</div>
        <div class="p-line"></div>
        <ul class="p-list">
          <li>ICP research &amp; definition</li>
          <li>CRM setup (HubSpot)</li>
          <li>Lead list build (500+ contacts)</li>
          <li>Cold email infrastructure &amp; warm-up</li>
          <li>Sequence copywriting</li>
          <li>Pipeline design</li>
          <li>Founder training &amp; handoff</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#go" class="p-btn p-btn-line">Book a free audit</a>
      </div>
      <div class="p-card pop sr sr-up" style="transition-delay:.06s">
        <div class="p-tag">Most founders start here</div>
        <div class="p-tier">Tier 2</div>
        <div class="p-name">RevOps Retainer</div>
        <div class="p-desc">Ongoing optimization, fresh campaigns, and someone who actually knows your pipeline.</div>
